BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:jHxeJC-jiwBcjYpO4xSi6
SUMMARY:Spring Equinox Gathering
DTSTAMP:20260318T234516Z
DTSTART:20260321T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Spring Equinox is a season of dynamic balance\, as we turn towa
	rd the energies of the East and all that is newly emerging in the earth an
	d in ourselves. There will be opportunities for meditation and for more em
	bodied engagement. Simple gathering and reflecting rituals will connect us
	 to the earth’s wisdom. We'll meet by the arch at Heritage Park. Be Prepar
	ed for the weather!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/sprin
