SUMMARY:Electoral Working Group Planning Subcommittee Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260318T234516Z
DTSTART:20260323T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Help us brainstorm\\\, research\\\, and plan for future elector
	al campaigns! We’re currently working on planning a potential campaign for
	 WA State House in the 37th LD. Some of the other tasks of this subcommitt
	ee include unified campaign ideation\\\, powermapping districts\\\, assess
	ing required scale of mobilization (field\\\, fundraising\\\, etc.) for po
	tential campaigns\\\, and candidate development and recruitment. \\n\\nSig
	n up for our weekly calendar event that contains the Zoom link using the f
	orm below! Email electoral@seattledsa.org with any questions.\n\nhttps://s
	eattledsa.org/event/electoral-working-group-planning-subcommittee-meeting-
